WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:01.949
Family, I'm excited to be with you all

00:00:01.959 --> 00:00:03.949
today. First off, I just want to say thank

00:00:03.959 --> 00:00:07.269
you for all of the likes, for

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:09.830
clicking the notification bell, and for

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:13.390
subscribing. It is helping to

00:00:13.390 --> 00:00:13.400
get

00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:15.430
the gospel out. There are so many

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:17.590
emails that I get telling me,

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:20.349
'Hey, I got born again today watching your

00:00:20.349 --> 00:00:20.359
video,'or

00:00:20.359 --> 00:00:22.830
'Hey, I got baptized in the Holy

00:00:22.840 --> 00:00:25.550
Ghost today watching your video.'I've heard from

00:00:25.550 --> 00:00:25.560
people who were

00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:27.990
set free from addictions—people

00:00:27.990 --> 00:00:28.000
who

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:29.509
were addicted to cigarettes

00:00:29.509 --> 00:00:29.519
and

00:00:29.519 --> 00:00:31.710
all

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:33.950
kinds of perversions who email me and

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:35.790
say

00:00:35.790 --> 00:00:35.800
they

00:00:35.800 --> 00:00:38.110
got set free. So I just want to let you

00:00:38.120 --> 00:00:40.670
know, thank you for all of your support.

00:00:40.680 --> 00:00:41.950
You know, there are a lot of people

00:00:41.950 --> 00:00:41.960
saying,

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:44.310
'Well, you're the only one seeing anything;

00:00:44.320 --> 00:00:46.150
you're the only one

00:00:46.150 --> 00:00:46.160
having

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:47.630
these visions, and nothing's

00:00:47.640 --> 00:00:50.229
come to pass.'I just started

00:00:50.239 --> 00:00:53.150
this

00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:55.510
YouTube channel back in March, and the Lord told

00:00:55.520 --> 00:00:57.189
me there’s going to be an

00:00:57.199 --> 00:00:59.470
acceleration of all things:

00:00:59.470 --> 00:00:59.480
acceleration

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:02.110
of the economy,

00:01:02.120 --> 00:01:04.950
acceleration in politics, and acceleration in

00:01:04.960 --> 00:01:07.310
spiritual things, like the signs in

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:09.830
the heavens. We are going to see some

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:13.429
amazing things in the days ahead.

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:16.469
No man knows the day or

00:01:16.479 --> 00:01:18.429
the hour when Jesus Christ is coming, but

00:01:18.439 --> 00:01:20.510
I can tell you I have an urgency in my

00:01:20.520 --> 00:01:22.350
spirit that He's coming. I have an

00:01:22.360 --> 00:01:24.469
urgency in my spirit to tell you it's

00:01:24.479 --> 00:01:27.230
time to repent, to get on our

00:01:27.240 --> 00:01:29.630
knees, and to seek the Lord with all our

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:32.350
hearts. We are in the last of the

00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:34.510
last seconds before the coming of the

00:01:34.520 --> 00:01:36.710
Lord Jesus Christ, and I want to

00:01:36.720 --> 00:01:39.990
encourage you today: don't give up on

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:41.990
your dreams, don't give up on what

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:44.350
God's called you to do. We've got to push.

00:01:44.360 --> 00:01:46.510
We're right at

00:01:46.520 --> 00:01:48.550
that one-yard line, right before first

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:50.749
and goal, and we're about to make a

00:01:50.759 --> 00:01:52.590
touchdown. As the

00:01:52.600 --> 00:01:54.950
body of Christ, we've got to stand and

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:58.190
be even stronger now than we've

00:01:58.200 --> 00:01:59.789
ever been before because

00:01:59.799 --> 00:02:02.670
great days are ahead for the

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:04.749
body of Christ. I want to

00:02:04.759 --> 00:02:06.149
give you that encouragement before I

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:07.950
tell you about the storms. There

00:02:07.950 --> 00:02:07.960
are

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:09.190
a lot of people talking about

00:02:09.200 --> 00:02:10.430
the storms. I've

00:02:10.440 --> 00:02:12.949
seen people on Sid Roth, and there are other

00:02:12.959 --> 00:02:14.790
prophetic people who have seen stuff,

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:16.990
but I was looking at people like Sister

00:02:16.990 --> 00:02:17.000
Billye.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:19.589
I told you all that I was caught

00:02:19.599 --> 00:02:21.710
up in the Spirit while I was praying

00:02:21.720 --> 00:02:23.509
one night, and I went before the throne.

00:02:23.519 --> 00:02:25.270
There was prayer circling in the

00:02:25.270 --> 00:02:25.280
throne—I'll

00:02:25.280 --> 00:02:27.630
put the video in the

00:02:27.640 --> 00:02:29.470
description below

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:30.869
if you're new to my

00:02:30.869 --> 00:02:30.879
channel—but

00:02:30.879 --> 00:02:34.229
there was a pastor that I

00:02:34.239 --> 00:02:36.790
saw whom I wasn't really familiar with.

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:38.990
I looked him up afterward and

00:02:38.990 --> 00:02:39.000
have kept

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:41.070
an eye on him

00:02:41.080 --> 00:02:43.430
to see what's going on in his ministry.

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:45.309
Whenever I was in the Spirit, the

00:02:45.319 --> 00:02:47.390
Lord showed me this pastor,

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:52.270
Tracy Harris, and he has a

00:02:52.280 --> 00:02:54.750
church in Texarkana. The Lord

00:02:54.760 --> 00:02:57.470
told me to follow his ministry

00:02:57.470 --> 00:02:57.480
regarding

00:02:57.480 --> 00:02:59.309
the end times. Then you

00:02:59.319 --> 00:03:03.390
go back to what Pastor Steve

00:03:03.390 --> 00:03:03.400
Cioccolanti

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:05.910
said; he talked about the pale,

00:03:05.910 --> 00:03:05.920
green-colored

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:08.750
horse—the

00:03:08.750 --> 00:03:08.760
warhorse—and

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:11.390
then the

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:14.990
plague would come after. Well,

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:17.309
like I said, we prophesy in

00:03:17.319 --> 00:03:19.390
part and hear in part. I see these things

00:03:19.400 --> 00:03:21.270
coming and I don't really know the dates,

00:03:21.280 --> 00:03:23.589
but

00:03:23.599 --> 00:03:25.670
I feel an urgency in my

00:03:25.670 --> 00:03:25.680
spirit. The Lord

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:28.589
will show you things way in

00:03:28.599 --> 00:03:31.869
advance.

00:03:31.879 --> 00:03:33.789
This prophecy from Sister

00:03:33.789 --> 00:03:33.799
Billye

00:03:33.799 --> 00:03:35.270
that

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:36.990
you're going to hear is about

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:39.110
a storm and the

00:03:39.110 --> 00:03:39.120
economy—something happening—and

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:41.149
then the next

00:03:41.159 --> 00:03:44.509
one we'll hear is about a plague

00:03:44.519 --> 00:03:48.309
coming greater than

00:03:48.319 --> 00:03:50.390
COVID.

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:52.710
Pastor John

00:03:52.720 --> 00:03:54.910
Kilpatrick had a visitation from the Lord in the

00:03:54.920 --> 00:03:57.429
midnight hour warning

00:03:57.439 --> 00:04:00.030
him about a storm coming.

00:04:00.040 --> 00:04:03.350
Many men of God are hearing

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:05.429
about a storm coming, and the Lord's

00:04:05.439 --> 00:04:07.550
warning them like little fire alarm

00:04:07.560 --> 00:04:09.390
bells going off:

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:12.910
'Caution, caution, caution.

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:15.270
Red alert.'There's a storm coming,

00:04:17.400 --> 00:04:20.270
but

00:04:20.280 --> 00:04:22.469
there'll be a calm after. There

00:04:22.469 --> 00:04:22.479
are

00:04:22.479 --> 00:04:25.870
going to be

00:04:25.880 --> 00:04:27.390
judgments.

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:33.510
You can sense things.

00:04:33.520 --> 00:04:37.870
We're not talking about the Great

00:04:37.870 --> 00:04:37.880
Tribulation—you

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:40.710
will not even be

00:04:40.710 --> 00:04:40.720
here—but

00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:43.469
here in the

00:04:43.479 --> 00:04:46.550
Ozarks, Shelly and I remember the ice storm years ago

00:04:48.870 --> 00:04:48.880
that

00:04:52.960 --> 00:04:55.870
knocked out electricity

00:04:55.880 --> 00:04:59.350
for two weeks. Trees broke everywhere.

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:02.670
I remember it

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:06.629
happened here in Oklahoma thirteen years ago.

00:05:06.639 --> 00:05:08.830
I had sold my house and

00:05:08.830 --> 00:05:08.840
was

00:05:08.840 --> 00:05:10.670
living in a double-wide with

00:05:10.670 --> 00:05:10.680
Shelly

00:05:10.680 --> 00:05:12.310
at Prayer Mountain until I could find

00:05:12.320 --> 00:05:15.270
another house. Terry

00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:18.550
and Lynn lived up over the

00:05:18.560 --> 00:05:20.909
firehouse.

00:05:20.919 --> 00:05:23.909
We had no

00:05:23.919 --> 00:05:26.670
heat, but we had a fireplace and lots of

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:28.990
wood, so we made a

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:33.550
fire.

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:43.070
We had iron cookware

00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:46.710
and

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:51.990
made oatmeal, boiled water,

00:05:51.990 --> 00:05:52.000
and

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:53.469
made

00:05:53.479 --> 00:05:57.830
chili. Terry would come down on the

00:05:57.840 --> 00:06:00.510
snowmobile and

00:06:00.520 --> 00:06:02.909
help us out;

00:06:02.909 --> 00:06:02.919
he's

00:06:02.919 --> 00:06:05.110
a survivor. For

00:06:05.120 --> 00:06:06.670
a while, they had a

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:09.110
generator.

00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:21.230
It was

00:06:21.240 --> 00:06:26.390
two weeks

00:06:26.390 --> 00:06:26.400
of

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:28.909
below-zero

00:06:28.909 --> 00:06:28.919
weather

00:06:28.919 --> 00:06:30.230
every night.

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:31.749
If you lived around

00:06:31.759 --> 00:06:32.710
here

00:06:32.710 --> 00:06:32.720
and

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:35.150
moved to town, town

00:06:35.160 --> 00:06:37.790
didn't have much better,

00:06:37.790 --> 00:06:37.800
though

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:40.990
they had some

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:45.670
fuel. Anyway, praise the Lord.

00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:49.390
I say pretend you're in the

00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:52.950
Ozarks and there could be an ice storm.

00:06:52.950 --> 00:06:52.960
It

00:06:52.960 --> 00:06:54.469
probably wouldn't last too long, maybe a few

00:06:54.479 --> 00:06:57.150
days, so it wouldn't hurt to

00:06:57.160 --> 00:07:00.350
keep your car filled with gas,

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:02.390
have a couple of extra cans,

00:07:02.390 --> 00:07:02.400
and

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:05.469
have plenty of

00:07:05.479 --> 00:07:08.869
water and food.

00:07:08.879 --> 00:07:10.830
I'm

00:07:10.840 --> 00:07:13.629
not a scare tactic person;

00:07:13.639 --> 00:07:15.830
I don't want you in fear. But it

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:19.070
doesn't hurt to have some

00:07:19.080 --> 00:07:22.990
peanut butter, tuna fish, salmon,

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:24.589
and things in cans that you don't have

00:07:24.599 --> 00:07:26.270
to fix for two or three

00:07:26.280 --> 00:07:28.309
days.

00:07:28.309 --> 00:07:28.319
I

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:30.909
just

00:07:30.919 --> 00:07:32.390
think it

00:07:32.400 --> 00:07:33.950
wouldn't be a bad idea. Besides,

00:07:33.960 --> 00:07:36.070
if nothing ever happens, you can eat it

00:07:36.070 --> 00:07:36.080
and

00:07:36.080 --> 00:07:38.029
drink the

00:07:38.039 --> 00:07:41.070
water! Glory be to God.

00:07:44.159 --> 00:07:45.830
You're

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:48.149
not going to throw any stones or

00:07:48.159 --> 00:07:50.350
tomatoes when

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:52.309
things

00:07:56.599 --> 00:07:57.869
happen according to

00:07:57.879 --> 00:07:59.790
God's calendar. She's telling

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:02.270
everybody, not in fear, to have a Psalm

00:08:02.270 --> 00:08:02.280
91 level

00:08:02.280 --> 00:08:04.510
of extra in your house.

00:08:04.520 --> 00:08:06.710
You can have an urgency like I'm

00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:08.469
talking about. When I was

00:08:08.479 --> 00:08:09.869
in the Spirit, the

00:08:09.879 --> 00:08:12.430
Lord showed me a massive storm coming on

00:08:12.440 --> 00:08:15.670
the East Coast. It was dark,

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:18.790
dark purple all inside,

00:08:22.159 --> 00:08:24.469
and every once in a while,

00:08:24.479 --> 00:08:26.029
the Lord shows

00:08:26.029 --> 00:08:26.039
it getting

00:08:26.039 --> 00:08:28.029
closer and closer.

00:08:28.039 --> 00:08:31.070
The last time I saw it, it was on our

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:35.310
shores. He showed me a

00:08:35.320 --> 00:08:37.709
massive, thick,

00:08:37.719 --> 00:08:41.350
humongous wall of protection.

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:43.870
He said this

00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:52.110
wall

00:08:52.120 --> 00:08:54.990
was

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:58.630
