00:09:07.680 --> 00:09:10.350
this is just like when it was

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:12.190
dark in Egypt and it was light in

00:09:12.190 --> 00:09:12.200
Goshen.

00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:15.350
He was telling me, 'This

00:09:15.360 --> 00:09:17.590
is Psalm.'There was a

00:09:17.600 --> 00:09:21.509
table

00:09:21.509 --> 00:09:21.519
prepared

00:09:21.519 --> 00:09:24.949
with dishes,

00:09:24.959 --> 00:09:26.430
bread, and

00:09:26.440 --> 00:09:29.509
