00:09:50.959 --> 00:09:53.150
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, I have

00:09:53.160 --> 00:09:55.470
prepared a table before you in the

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:58.750
presence of all your

00:09:58.750 --> 00:09:58.760
enemies.'He

00:09:58.760 --> 00:10:00.670
said in the days

00:10:00.680 --> 00:10:02.990
ahead,

00:10:03.000 --> 00:10:06.230
you will have to have a

00:10:06.240 --> 00:10:09.949
revelation of the name, the power, and

00:10:09.959 --> 00:10:12.030
the authority of the name of Jesus.

00:10:12.040 --> 00:10:13.870
You're going to have to know

00:10:13.880 --> 00:10:17.470
that you need to get Psalm 91 and

00:10:17.470 --> 00:10:17.480
Psalm

00:10:17.480 --> 00:10:20.949
23 deep down in your

00:10:20.959 --> 00:10:24.269
heart. Put it so deep down inside of you

00:10:24.279 --> 00:10:25.670
that you don't

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:27.470
question it. It's like it's a rhema word to

00:10:27.480 --> 00:10:29.269
you; that is what I'm talking about. You can

00:10:29.279 --> 00:10:31.829
read the word, but you have to know the

00:10:31.839 --> 00:10:34.670
word. You have to have a revelation

00:10:34.680 --> 00:10:37.269
knowledge of the word. You can just go

00:10:37.279 --> 00:10:38.949
through Genesis and read it and read it

00:10:38.959 --> 00:10:41.389
and read it, but the devil knows when you

00:10:41.399 --> 00:10:44.310
know. I'm telling you, I've seen it; I

00:10:44.320 --> 00:10:45.990
know in the spirit

00:10:45.990 --> 00:10:46.000
realm

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:49.310
when that sword comes out

00:10:49.320 --> 00:10:52.350
of your mouth and it cuts the devil.

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:54.990
It's either alive inside of you

