or it's not. You can quote it and

00:10:57.240 --> 00:10:58.430
quote it and quote

00:10:58.430 --> 00:10:58.440
it—and

00:10:58.440 --> 00:11:00.069
faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by

00:11:00.079 --> 00:11:02.949
the word of God. That's how you get

00:11:02.949 --> 00:11:02.959
rhema

00:11:02.959 --> 00:11:06.710
word inside of you: by

00:11:06.720 --> 00:11:08.949
hearing and hearing and hearing and

00:11:08.959 --> 00:11:10.710
