00:11:15.629 --> 00:11:15.639
sits

00:11:15.639 --> 00:11:17.190
there, and it spits up out of

00:11:17.190 --> 00:11:17.200
its

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:19.910
stomach and it chews on that grass

00:11:19.920 --> 00:11:22.670
again. You've got to keep that word

00:11:22.680 --> 00:11:25.470
inside of your mouth, and it's

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:28.230
what brings life. That's whenever

00:11:28.240 --> 00:11:30.550
your mountain needs to hear

00:11:30.560 --> 00:11:33.310
your voice. You have to speak to your

00:11:33.320 --> 00:11:34.990
circumstances, and that's what I'm

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:37.470
