00:11:37.480 --> 00:11:40.030
the believer and having a

00:11:40.040 --> 00:11:42.629
revelation of the name of Jesus,

00:11:42.639 --> 00:11:45.230
understanding who we are in Christ,

00:11:45.230 --> 00:11:45.240
seated

00:11:45.240 --> 00:11:47.230
with Him in the heavenlies, far above all

00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:49.069
principalities and powers and might. It's

00:11:49.079 --> 00:11:50.629
not going to come just by hearing it

00:11:50.639 --> 00:11:52.269
once; it's not just going to come by

00:11:52.279 --> 00:11:54.910
hearing it twice. Faith comes by

00:11:54.920 --> 00:11:56.670
hearing, and hearing, and hearing

00:11:56.680 --> 00:11:59.389
by the word of God, getting that

00:11:59.399 --> 00:12:02.030
revelation inside of you of where we are

00:12:02.040 --> 00:12:04.030
in these end times. The Lord told me,

00:12:04.040 --> 00:12:07.389
'Sobering days are coming. Very

00:12:07.399 --> 00:12:10.350
sobering days, very hard days for some

00:12:10.350 --> 00:12:10.360
people.'But

